Gameplay


















Capture all the colored blocks
Each color block you capture earns you another point. Get as many as you can then escape through the exit. Don't miss any or they will count against your score.











Simple and Addictive
Paper Trail is very simple in concept, but more challenging than you think. Can you beat your high score? You'll soon realize you can't stop playing.






About Us













Dragon Army is a mobile game studio based in Atlanta, GA.
The team at Dragon Army consists of developers, designers, and marketers that have come together with one idea in mind:
bring the best in gaming to mobile devices everywhere.
